## üí¨ 5. **Sample Conversation Flow**

### **Scenario:** User wants to renew motor insurance.

**User:**
‚ÄúHi, I need to renew my car insurance before the month ends.‚Äù

**Agent:**
‚ÄúGot it! Can you please confirm your car registration number?‚Äù

**User:**
‚ÄúKDC 874N‚Äù

**Agent:**
‚ÄúThanks! I found your last cover with Jubilee Insurance expiring on 29th Oct.
Would you like to renew the same policy or compare with other providers?‚Äù

**User:**
‚ÄúCompare with others.‚Äù

**Agent:**
‚ÄúHere are top 3 motor insurance options for you:
1Ô∏è‚É£ Jubilee ‚Äî KES 9,800 (Comprehensive, same as before)
2Ô∏è‚É£ Britam ‚Äî KES 9,200 (Comprehensive, includes towing)
3Ô∏è‚É£ Madison ‚Äî KES 8,700 (Third-party + theft cover)

Which option would you like to proceed with?‚Äù

**User:**
‚ÄúBritam looks good.‚Äù

**Agent:**
‚ÄúExcellent choice. I‚Äôll initiate renewal with Britam.
Would you like to pay via M-Pesa?‚Äù

**User:**
‚ÄúYes.‚Äù

**Agent:**
‚ÄúProcessing... ‚úÖ Payment received.
Your new cover is active until 21 Oct 2026. I‚Äôve also saved it in your portal and set a renewal reminder.‚Äù

