## üß± 6. **System Integration Prototype**

| Component           | Example Implementation          |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| **Frontend**        | WhatsApp bot or Web form        |
| **Backend**         | Node.js / Python Flask API      |
| **Database**        | PostgreSQL (policy + user data) |
| **Payment**         | M-Pesa STK Push API             |
| **AI Engine**       | GPT-based agent orchestrator    |
| **Document Engine** | PDF generator for policies      |
| **Notifications**   | Twilio / WhatsApp Cloud API     |

